01:24:02.410 --> 01:24:05.560
Found him hanging in his room.

01:24:10.420 --> 01:24:12.350
Jesus.

01:24:13.320 --> 01:24:16.380
- Did he leave a note?
- No.

01:24:43.150 --> 01:24:49.959
My father gave it to me when
