01:25:05.540 --> 01:25:07.200
Confession.

01:25:15.920 --> 01:25:19.220
Bonner's car. What color is it?

01:25:20.190 --> 01:25:22.850
Blue. Why?

01:25:33.340 --> 01:25:36.839
You don't kill someone for no reason.
