01:27:35.520 --> 01:27:37.320
That's good.

01:27:37.960 --> 01:27:39.620
That's good.

01:28:54.370 --> 01:28:58.239
The remains will be shipped this afternoon.
Check the address of the funeral home.

01:28:58.240 --> 01:28:59.469
That's correct.

01:28:59.470 --> 01:29:04.680
If I can be of any other help,
just let me know.

01:30:07.980 --> 01:30:09.000
Sir?

01:30:13.150 --> 01:30:15.880
You got any jumper cables?

01:30:24.990 --> 01:30:26.460
