01:30:30.400 --> 01:30:35.669
I wanted to say how sorry I am
for what happened to Mike.

01:30:35.670 --> 01:30:41.039
And I wanted to apologize for lying
about not seeing him that night.

01:30:41.040 --> 01:30:48.510
I just thought that if I were Mike,
I wouldn't want my parents to know.

01:30:49.220 --> 01:30:52.380
- You got a cigarette?
- Yeah.

01:31:10.340 --> 01:31:13.240
You think Bonner killed him?

01:31:14.780 --> 01:31:16.330
No.

01:31:17.580 --> 01:31:19.380
I don't know.

01:31:21.250 --> 01:31:24.550
I don't understand any of this.

01:31:25.790 --> 01:31:27.789
What would he have against my boy?

01:31:27.790 --> 01:31:29.380
Nothing.

01:31:31.230 --> 01:31:32.750
I'm sorry.

01:31:35.930 --> 01:31:39.799
- Mike tell you much about Bosnia?
- Some.

01:31:39.800 --> 01:31:46.369
We seemed to always pull sentry duty
together. Freezing our asses off.

01:31:46.370 --> 01:31:48.479
He tried to convince me
of crazy things.

01:31:48.480 --> 01:31:50.609
Try to get you to wear pantyhose?

01:31:50.610 --> 01:31:52.749
- Did he tell you?
- No, I told him.

01:31:52.750 --> 01:31:56.070
Cuts the cold like nothing else.

01:31:56.420 --> 01:31:57.989
So he wasn't lying?

01:31:57.990 --> 01:32:05.990
You don't want to get shot wearing
a pair of those. You'll never live it down.

01:32:25.950 --> 01:32:28.319
It's fucked up, isn't it?

01:32:28.320 --> 01:32:29.780
Yeah.

01:32:54.980 --> 01:32:57.179
<i>Let's get you to a good
American hospital.</i>

01:32:57.180 --> 01:32:59.879
<i>Come on, speed this thing up!</i>

01:32:59.880 --> 01:33:03.170
<i>It's okay. I'm gonna help you.</i>

01:33:03.790 --> 01:33:05.849
<i>It's okay. Take it easy.</i>

01:33:05.850 --> 01:33:09.570
<i>We're gonna take care of you, okay?</i>

01:33:12.690 --> 01:33:15.250
<i>You okay? You all right?</i>

01:33:16.100 --> 01:33:19.920
<i>Now, where does it hurt? Right there?</i>

01:33:20.640 --> 01:33:22.800
<i>Easy. Right there?</i>

01:33:23.200 --> 01:33:26.920
<i>We're gonna take care of you, okay?</i>

01:34:03.610 --> 01:34:05.040
Good night.

01:35:04.140 --> 01:35:08.779
Tell me that's your son's signature
on his credit-card receipt.

01:35:08.780 --> 01:35:10.770
No, it is not.

01:35:11.180 --> 01:35:13.910
We always assumed Mike was there.

01:35:13.920 --> 01:35:16.319
That's Penning's signature.

01:35:16.320 --> 01:35:20.150
Three meals. Penning, Bonner and Long.

01:35:55.960 --> 01:35:59.229
Penning and Long. I want them now.

01:35:59.230 --> 01:36:04.529
