01:39:06.150 --> 01:39:07.550
Yeah.

01:39:10.420 --> 01:39:12.819
And your friends didn't try and stop you?

01:39:12.820 --> 01:39:16.380
I think they were sort of stunned.

01:39:16.760 --> 01:39:18.359
They're yelling.

01:39:18.360 --> 01:39:23.080
And Mike falls to the ground,
and he's dead.

01:39:23.230 --> 01:39:28.550
And Long is screaming,
"Christ, what do we do now?"

01:39:28.940 --> 01:39:32.439
It was Bonner's idea to chop him up.

01:39:32.440 --> 01:39:35.179
He used to work for a butcher.

01:39:35.180 --> 01:39:40.579
He knew how to work the knife
around the joints. Made it easier.

01:39:40.580 --> 01:39:43.419
We would've buried the parts...

01:39:43.420 --> 01:39:48.400
...but it was getting late
and we hadn't eaten.

01:39:49.020 --> 01:39:50.960
You were hungry?

01:39:51.130 --> 01:39:52.680
Starving.

01:39:54.700 --> 01:39:58.010
We stopped at the Chicken Shack.

01:39:59.970 --> 01:40:02.680
I liked Mike, we all did.

01:40:03.800 --> 01:40:11.779
But I think on another night that would've
been Mike with the knife and me in the field.

01:40:11.780 --> 01:40:14.910
I think he was the smart one.

01:40:16.320 --> 01:40:18.620
I think he could see.

01:40:22.590 --> 01:40:24.890
I'm truly sorry, sir.

01:40:26.430 --> 01:40:29.060
I'm sorry for your loss.

01:40:38.670 --> 01:40:41.270
I saw a video Mike shot.

01:40:41.280 --> 01:40:44.320
Him in the back of a Humvee.

01:40:47.450 --> 01:40:52.110
Looked like he was
torturing a prisoner or...

