We arrested some haji
who was wounded.

01:41:02.830 --> 01:41:05.650
And we were riding along...

01:41:05.730 --> 01:41:08.669
...and Mike was pretending
like he was a medic.

01:41:08.670 --> 01:41:13.869
And he would stick his hand
in this guy's wound...

01:41:13.870 --> 01:41:16.679
...and he says, "Does this hurt?"

01:41:16.680 --> 01:41:20.340
And the haji screamed, "Yeah, yeah."

01:41:20.980 --> 01:41:24.819
And then Mike would stick his hand
in the exact same place...

01:41:24.820 --> 01:41:27.810
...and say, "Does that hurt?"

01:41:31.790 --> 01:41:33.940
It was pretty funny.

01:41:37.060 --> 01:41:40.040
It became a thing with Mike.

01:41:41.740 --> 01:41:45.280
That's how he got the name "Doc."

01:41:46.240 --> 01:41:49.110
It was just a way to cope.

01:41:50.010 --> 01:41:52.660
We all did stupid things.

01:42:35.720 --> 01:42:37.710
Excuse me, sir.

01:42:56.110 --> 01:43:00.260
You know where Private Ortiez's room is?

01:43:08.860 --> 01:43:10.740
You got a minute?

01:43:13.490 --> 01:43:15.959
