01:44:29.040 --> 01:44:31.340
Why would he do that?

01:44:38.210 --> 01:44:42.170
I don't know what anybody's told you.

01:44:42.850 --> 01:44:45.080
There are standing orders.

01:44:45.090 --> 01:44:46.889
You're in a convoy...

01:44:46.890 --> 01:44:50.089
