01:45:45.250 --> 01:45:47.110
...we hit a kid.

01:45:47.650 --> 01:45:49.780
I don't believe it.

01:45:49.920 --> 01:45:51.940
You ask me...

01:45:53.950 --> 01:45:55.820
...we hit a dog.

01:45:57.930 --> 01:46:00.020
