01:46:03.530 --> 01:46:06.400
I don't know what that is.

01:46:08.640 --> 01:46:10.700
No fucking idea.

01:46:36.400 --> 01:46:39.799
Hey, Bonner, there's your family.

01:46:39.800 --> 01:46:42.169
- Stop fucking around!
- It's a fucking phone.

01:46:42.170 --> 01:46:45.000
- You could have broken it.
- You're a fucking idiot.

01:46:45.010 --> 01:46:46.060
Oh, fuck.

01:46:46.970 --> 01:46:49.509
- Oh, shit.
- Do not stop! Do not fucking stop!

01:46:49.510 --> 01:46:53.490
- What do I do?
- Speed up! Speed up!

01:47:00.850 --> 01:47:03.359
<i>- What are you doing?
- Dad?</i>

01:47:03.360 --> 01:47:06.089
Get back in the fucking vehicle, Mike!

01:47:06.090 --> 01:47:09.259
Mike, get back in the fucking vehicle!

01:47:09.260 --> 01:47:10.700
<i>Daddy?</i>

01:47:18.070 --> 01:47:21.130
Let's go, Mike, now!

01:47:21.910 --> 01:47:24.140
<i>Are you there, Daddy?</i>

01:47:24.750 --> 01:47:27.130
I can hardly hear you.

01:47:28.620 --> 01:47:31.750
You gotta get me out of here.

01:47:32.450 --> 01:47:35.860
Well, that's just nerves talking.

01:47:37.360 --> 01:47:39.850
Something happened, Dad.

01:47:49.040 --> 01:47:51.010
For Christ's sake.

01:47:53.940 --> 01:47:56.670
Is anybody there with you?

01:47:58.410 --> 01:48:00.040
No, I'm alone.

01:48:03.620 --> 01:48:05.140
That's good.

01:48:06.990 --> 01:48:09.790
Okay, Daddy, I gotta go.

01:48:11.990 --> 01:48:13.890
You be safe, son.

01:48:14.060 --> 01:48:15.790
Stay safe.

01:48:17.160 --> 01:48:20.000
Yeah. You too.

01:48:49.130 --> 01:48:53.499
You know, my son's been driving me crazy
ever since you came over.

01:48:53.500 --> 01:48:55.760
He wants a slingshot.

01:49:00.310 --> 01:49:04.940
Guess it could be worse.
Could be a BB gun.

01:49:30.670 --> 01:49:31.810
Thank you.

01:51:24.080 --> 01:51:27.649
<i>So every day,
Goliath would walk into the valley...</i>

01:51:27.650 --> 01:51:31.180
...to challenge someone, anyone.

01:51:31.860 --> 01:51:34.750
But no one would fight him.

01:51:34.800 --> 01:51:37.159
Until David showed up...

01:51:37.160 --> 01:51:40.169
...and said, "You know what?
I'll do it. I'll fight him."

01:51:40.170 --> 01:51:44.169
So the king dressed David up
in his own armor, which was so big...

01:51:44.170 --> 01:51:48.300
But why would he let him fight a giant?

01:51:48.510 --> 01:51:50.550
He was just a boy.

01:51:53.280 --> 01:51:55.930
I don't know, sweetheart.

01:51:57.380 --> 01:52:00.270
Do you think he was scared?

01:52:00.750 --> 01:52:01.780
David?

01:52:07.730 --> 01:52:09.360
<i>Yeah.</i>

01:52:09.660 --> 01:52:13.900
<i>I think he would have been really scared.</i>

01:53:03.720 --> 01:53:06.749
- Just like that?
- Just like that.

01:53:06.750 --> 01:53:08.900
It looks really old.

01:53:09.690 --> 01:53:11.910
It's been well used.

01:53:22.240 --> 01:53:24.269
And I shouldn't take it down at night?

01:53:24.270 --> 01:53:25.830
No.

01:53:27.440 --> 01:53:30.420
You leave it just like that.

01:53:31.240 --> 01:53:33.460
That's a lot easier.
